image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a narrow, winding staircase inside a building. The stairs are covered in a dark grey, patterned carpet (grid/square pattern). On the left, there is a blue metal railing with a wooden handrail. The walls are painted an off-white or light beige color. A single, round, glowing light fixture is mounted on the wall above the stairs. An electrical outlet is visible on the wall near the turn of the stairs.
image_analysis.layout: Vertical composition focusing on the upward path of the staircase.
